episodes.title: From HINDU CULT to CATHOLICISM — Her SHOCKING Journey!
episodes.description:
00:00- Intro
1:25 - Childhood & Early Formation 
7:56 - Moving to America 
11:31- The Influence of Catholic School 
14:15 - Marriage & Opening Up Conversations 
16:43 - Karma & Astrology 
19:19 - Pregnancy & Health 
27:46 - Waking Up 
32:52 - Search for Truth & Catholic Influences 
41:01 - OCIA
50:11 - Final Thoughts 

Shana’s incredible journey takes her from the depths of the Sai Baba Hindu cult to the joy of entering the Catholic Church just one year ago. In this interview, she opens up about the beliefs she once held in the cult—and how, step by step, God led her to the fullness of truth. You won’t want to miss her powerful story.
